IMDB backend to Movie Pole (IMRb 0.0 - Jakub KuÅºma 2008)

usage:

IMDB.new.movies(:year => 2008)
IMDB.new.movies(:year => 1999..2003)
IMDB.new.movies(:rating => 6) # with rating >= 6
IMDB.new.movies(:rating => 6..8) # with rating between 6 and 8
IMDB.new.movies(:votes => 1000) # with number of votes >= 1000
IMDB.new.movies(:keywords => "beer monkey") # including keywords "beer" and "monkey"
